        "created_at": "2025-12-28T16:20:12.104Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Signal‚Äôs not designed for large groups. If you have enough people in a Signal group, the security value of it is no longer relevant. There was a real-world example where the admin of an immigrant rights group added the FBI, and then members were arrested.</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2025/nov/21/fbi-signal-group-chat-immigration\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/7/1/718a4f1a8f5d12c5b566fc2a67a1b6fa08ac103a.png\" class=\"site-icon\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"4F6890\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2025/nov/21/fbi-signal-group-chat-immigration\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"04:35PM - 21 November 2025\">the Guardian ‚Äì 21 Nov 25</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    \n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2025/nov/21/fbi-signal-group-chat-immigration\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The FBI spied on a Signal group chat of immigration activists, records reveal</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Exclusive: Agency accessed private conversations of New York ‚Äòcourtwatch‚Äô group that was observing public hearings</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
