        "created_at": "2025-12-28T21:13:54.191Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This also sounds more like a forum model rather than what I would expect from a messenger. In a private group chat, I think it makes sense to set permissions manually and not by some (arbitrary) number of days.</p>",
