        "created_at": "2026-01-10T22:15:25.085Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I don‚Äôt see how that‚Äôs so. With reasonable privacy settings (do not show my phone number to anyone), how can anyone identify folks in a group? It seems to me that there still is plenty of privacy value in large groups.</p>\n<p>I admin a couple ~200 member groups and the inability of moderators to delete abusive/inappropriate messages is the biggest killjoy from my POV.</p>\n<p>OP‚Äôs automated moderation system sounds like potentially a good idea if possibly a bit heavy handed.</p>",
