        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/e/41988e/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2026-01-11T09:32:58.871Z",
        "cooked": "<p>My two cents:</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Avitus\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"73878\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/avitus/48/34172_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Avitus:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Signal‚Äôs not designed for large groups.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Signal is designed for groups of up to 1000 people and should have the necessary features to make that viable.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Alex7511\" data-post=\"6\" data-topic=\"73878\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/edb3f5/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Alex7511:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>possibly a bit heavy handed</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>A less heavy feature to make groups of these sizes feasible is this one, which I think would be a good start and less complicated to implement:</p>\n<aside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"22229\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/c/db5fbb/48.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <div class=\"quote-title__text-content\">\n      <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/ability-for-group-admins-to-delete-any-message-for-everyone/22229\">Ability for group admins to delete any message for everyone</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/17\"><span data-category-id=\"17\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #83B72A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --style-square \" title=\"Post your ideas here for new features and functionality for the Signal app.\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    Hi, please can you add the facility when a group has been setup if a admin wants to remove a comment/chat from the group they can remove from everyone.\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n",
