        "created_at": "2026-01-11T17:58:32.525Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Semantics. My point was that although it is (I guess not) designed for it, it usually isn‚Äôt viable to have groups of those sizes (which is the problem I think we all want to solve).</p>\n<p>The discussion should be what features are potentially missing to make large group chats more viable, and I believe the one I linked is a good start. (There are plenty of other features as well, including this one, but you have to start somewhere. Also, Signal wouldn‚Äôt keep increasing the group limits unless they were intending for larger groups to be formed.)</p>",
